---
import Layout from "layouts/Layout.astro";
import Projects from 'components/projects/Projects'
---

<Layout title="hello world!">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-lg px-3 py-6">
		<div class="flex flex-col items-center md:flex-row md:justify-between md:gap-x-24">
			<div>

				<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold"><img src="/img/memoji.png" class=" -ml-4 h-32 inline-block" alt=""> <span
						class="-ml-6">hi, i'm <span
							class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-200 to-teal-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Brilyan</span></span>
				</h1>
				<p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-9 text-justify">
					i'm a full-stack developer who likes to build things. i'm currently working on a <a href="https://uns.ac.id"
						class="text-transparent hover:animate-pulse bg-clip-text bg-green-200 hover:bg-gradient-to-tr hover:from-blue-500 hover:to-blue-300 hover:font-bold hover:uppercase">Universitas
						Sebelas Maret</a> and
					<a href="https://wiyata.id" target="_blank"
						class="text-transparent  hover:animate-pulse bg-clip-text bg-green-200 hover:bg-gradient-to-tr hover:from-fuchsia-500 hover:to-purple-300 hover:font-bold hover:uppercase">Wiyata
						Academy</a>.
					i'm also an undergraduate informatics student at Universitas Sebelas Maret.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-9 text-justify">
					i started coding when i was at first year in university. my first programming language is Python 🐍. At first
					it was just a class subject, but i was interested in it and i started to learn it by myself and deep dive into
					it.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="shrink-0">
				<img class="h-64 w-64 hidden sm:block  animate-spin-slow"
					src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/a7/React-icon.svg" alt="Avatar image" loading="lazy">
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-lg px-3 py-6">
		<div class="mb-6 text-2xl font-bold">Recent <span
				class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-emerald-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Projects</span></div>
		<Projects client:visible />
	</div>
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-lg px-3 py-6">
		<div class="mb-6 text-2xl font-bold">Contact <span
				class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-emerald-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Me</span>
		</div>
		<div class="flex flex-col items-center md:flex-row md:justify-between md:gap-x-24">
			<a href="mailto:619mistico@gmail.com">Mail</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>